Author: peach_milk8
Text: Honestly its true nickacado was so skinny and he even notices it too! He knows he shouldn't be eating stuff like that but he still does it and its crazy how someone could eat so much! He's 27 or 28 and he says hes going to stop and "get healthy" at 30 but at the rate he's going I bet he won't change anything and thats kinda spooky
